metadata.name: Blood in Pointe Shoes
metadata.description:
She seemed to be made of moonlight, mysteriously illuminating the scene. The audience involuntarily pressed into their theirs, embraced by an alarmingly admiring sense of unreality of what was happening: she was floating in the air.
The story of the life and work of ballerina  is very similar to the well-known fairy tale about the unexpected transformation of a duckling into a swan. The only difference in this plot is that the miraculous transformation was realized not by the "will of fate", but thanks to his own willpower and inexhaustible inspiration...
